#🌾 OptiCrop: Smart Agricultural Production Optimization Engine

##📌 Project Description
OptiCrop is a machine learning-based system that recommends the most suitable crop to grow based on soil and environmental conditions — Nitrogen (N), Phosphorous (P), Potassium (K), temperature, humidity, pH, and rainfall. It combines a trained ML model with a Flask web app, so a user enters these values and instantly gets the best crop recommendation, helping improve yield and resource use.

